Package com.jacobschneider.engine.math.boundingvolumes

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OverlapStrategy
    An interface for an overlap strategy.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoundCircle  
    BoundNull
    Empty BoundVolume class whose overlap strategies always return true.
    BoundSphere  
    BoundVolume
    Represents a bounding volume around a physical object (usually a Shape object).
    BoundVolumePair
    This class represents an unordered pair of BoundVolume types.
    OverlapStrategyContainer
    This is a static class that contains all the OverlapStrategy implementations that are apart of the original engine.
